computer : Phenom 3.13.0-91-generic #138-Ubuntu SMP Fri Jun 24 17:00:34 UTC 2016 x86_64 GNU/Linux
operator : leo
option   : 15 1
stop     : Fri Jul  1 22:08:27 UTC 2016
